ent browser, it was more of the same.<\/p>\n<p>With last night&#8217;s announcement of <a href=\"http:\/\/googleblog.blogspot.com\/2008\/09\/fresh-take-on-browser.html\">Google&#8217;s New Chrome Browser<\/a>, they put up a nice <a href=\"http:\/\/www.google.com\/googlebooks\/chrome\/\">little <\/a>webcomic that explains the features it offers.\u00a0\u00a0 The security, privacy, and performance enhancements alone make this a must-watch for browsers.\u00a0 When it is actually released later today, we&#8217;ll see how I feel then.<\/p>\n<p><strong>UPDATE:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Found <a href=\"http:\/\/blogoscoped.com\/archive\/2008-09-02-n72.html\">a site that has some Chrome screenshots<\/a> you may enjoy.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>It&#8217;s been a long time since I&#8217;ve been excited about a new browser.\u00a0 Theoretically, I&#8217;ve never been excited about a new browser that was announced.\u00a0\u00a0 I remember being excited when AOL resurrected Netscape &#8211; but &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":97594,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[2],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3212"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3212"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3212\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/97594"}],"wp:attachm